Jeremy Clarkson was fired from Top Gear in March after attacking a producer during filming . 
  Today he gave his 'heartfelt thanks' to those who have supported him . 
  Former presenter Angela Rippon said she would be keen to return to the show . 
  BBC bosses are said to be trying to persuade Richard Hammond and James May to continue . 
  Clarkson said he would 'miss' fronting the BBC2 show . 
  He was fired after attacking producer Oisin Tymon in March . 
 